reviews.review_text: 2nd best sbd This is the second best sbd out there the only reason I say this is not cuz you can hear the crowd but cuz it seems to be toned down but it could be fix.I like hearing the crowd but its seems quieter than the other sbd out there that I ranked as number 1.But I give this 4 for the sound & 4 for the show still.
